"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-olympian-phelps-suspended-for-3-months-over-marijuana\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  KATHMANDU, Feb 6: The great swimming sensation and all time high Olympic gold medalist Michael Phelps was suspended from competition for three months by USA Swimming, the latest fallout from a photo that showed the Olympic great inhaling from a marijuana pipe.The Associated Press (AP) reported rfom Colorado Springs, Colorado that the US sport\\u00b4s national governing body also cut off its financial support to Phelps for the same three-month period, effective Thursday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.806732390216005e-32, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 168, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999906078756, \"rank\": 7.275106437453877e-09, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9992157964171207, \"rank\": 0.0007107627548948036, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 3